# WEB.rules

• Prefer React‑Server Components (app router) when possible; mark Client Components explicitly.
• No inline styles—use Tailwind classes exclusively.
• Wallet flow: wrap `_app.tsx` with ConnectionProvider → WalletProvider → WalletModalProvider.
• Never query RPCs directly inside components—fetch via hooks (SWR / tRPC).
• Type all public keys as `PublicKey` (from `@solana/web3.js`), not `string`.
• Pages ≤ 150 LOC; move heavy logic to hooks or utilities.
• `pnpm lint && pnpm typecheck` must pass locally and in CI.

Cursor Pattern Matches:
web/**/*.ts, web/**/*.tsx, web/**/*.json, *.md
